    <h1 class="hr-header">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>

    <h4>What is Din?</h4>
    <p>Din preps ingredients so you can cook restaurant meals at home. Our freshly prepared ingredients enable you to cook faster with more flavor and wider variety. Din is a service for people who are short on time and want to cook quality meals at home. With Din, you can stop wasting time figuring out what to make, searching for parking at the grocery store and throwing away food that goes bad before you get a chance to eat it.</p>
    <p>Din is faster than the grocery store, better than takeout, and cheaper than a restaurant.</p>

